    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Welcome"><a href="#Welcome" class="headerlink" title="Welcome"></a>Welcome</h1><p>Welcome! This blog is powered by <a href="https://pages.github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Pages</a> and <a href="https://hexo.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo</a>.</p><p>This post is for testing purpose only.</p><h1 id="Tests"><a href="#Tests" class="headerlink" title="Tests"></a>Tests</h1><h2 id="Basic-Tests"><a href="#Basic-Tests" class="headerlink" title="Basic Tests"></a>Basic Tests</h2><p><a href="/history/index.html">Test History (Implementing <code>Timeline</code>)</a></p><p>Test math formula: $a\in R_q$.</p><p>C Code highlighting:</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d\n"</span>, <span class="number">233</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://imys.net/custom/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Indigo customization</a></p><blockquote><p>Quoted quote.</p></blockquote><p>Comments to quoted text</p><h2 id="Figure"><a href="#Figure" class="headerlink" title="Figure"></a>Figure</h2><p><del>Use HTML <code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> tag to include a figure, instead of Markdown’s <code>![Apple HomePod](https://www.apple.com/v/home/do/images/promos/homepod_film_large.jpg &quot;Apple HomePod&quot;)</code> to provide better experience.</del></p><p>Two different approaches to include figure</p><h3 id="Markdown"><a href="#Markdown" class="headerlink" title="Markdown"></a>Markdown</h3><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://www.apple.com/v/home/do/images/promos/homepod_film_large.jpg" alt="Apple HomePod - 1" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">Apple HomePod - 1</div>            </figure><p>Code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">Apple HomePod - 1</span>](<span class="link">https://www.apple.com/v/home/do/images/promos/homepod_film_large.jpg</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="HTML"><a href="#HTML" class="headerlink" title="HTML"></a>HTML</h3><figure class="image-bubble"><div class="img-lightbox"><div class="overlay"></div><img src="https://www.apple.com/v/home/do/images/promos/homepod_film_large.jpg" alt="image"></div><div class="image-caption">Apple HomePod - 2</div></figure><p>Code:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">figure</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"image-bubble"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"img-lightbox"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"overlay"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://www.apple.com/v/home/do/images/promos/homepod_film_large.jpg"</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">"image"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"image-caption"</span>&gt;</span>Apple HomePod - 2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">figure</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Card-Style-Test"><a href="#Card-Style-Test" class="headerlink" title="Card Style Test"></a>Card Style Test</h3><div class="card"><p>为了解决 Hexo 自定义页面<code>slug</code>为空不能很好的使用多说评论这个问题，现在已经给每个自定义页面自动生成了<code>hexo-page-path</code>这种格式的<code>slug</code>。<br>本来准备用<code>date</code>做格式的最后一节，测试中发现 page 中的<code>date</code>值为修改时间，是动态的。<br>综合考虑使用了路径<code>path</code>。</p><p>以后可以根据需要添加更多模块支持。</p><p>打赏和评论默认开启，可根据需要在 Markdown 头部定义是否关闭。</p></div><hr><h1 id="Useful-Commands"><a href="#Useful-Commands" class="headerlink" title="Useful Commands"></a>Useful Commands</h1><h2 id="Clean-Generate-and-Initiate-Local-Server"><a href="#Clean-Generate-and-Initiate-Local-Server" class="headerlink" title="Clean, Generate and Initiate Local Server"></a>Clean, Generate and Initiate Local Server</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Commit-to-GitHub"><a href="#Commit-to-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="Commit to GitHub"></a>Commit to GitHub</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d -m <span class="string">"Add commit message here"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
